1
00:00:01,130 --> 00:00:02,130
Um, Makoto...

2
00:00:02,130 --> 00:00:04,750
Hm? Is there something on my face again?

3
00:00:04,750 --> 00:00:05,840
Oh, no, it's nothing.

4
00:00:05,840 --> 00:00:07,340
Oh! Right, Yuki.

5
00:00:07,340 --> 00:00:08,340
What is it?

6
00:00:08,340 --> 00:00:10,840
I heard from Natsu-san
about the whole "fake couple" thing.

7
00:00:10,840 --> 00:00:12,260
Huh? I didn't tell you?

8
00:00:12,260 --> 00:00:16,390
You didn't.
Um, it's okay if you don't want to talk about it...

9
00:00:17,020 --> 00:00:19,480
Yuki, why are you
pretending to be a couple?

10
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:20,770
It's because...

11
00:00:21,440 --> 00:00:24,770
Never mind.
If you don't want to talk about it, don't force yourself.

12
00:00:24,770 --> 00:00:27,650
Sorry, I'll tell you later.

13
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,780
(He must have his reasons.
I shouldn't push him.)

14
00:00:31,780 --> 00:00:33,240
Yuki, what time is your class today?

15
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:34,280
Afternoon.

16
00:00:34,280 --> 00:00:34,840
Same here.

17
00:00:35,030 --> 00:00:38,160
It's a bit of a rush to go home now.
Can I borrow your shower and some clothes?

18
00:00:38,160 --> 00:00:42,380
Yeah, the bathroom's over there.
Just grab any towel.

19
00:00:42,380 --> 00:00:43,670
Okay, thanks.

20
00:00:43,670 --> 00:00:44,790
Yeah.

21
00:00:48,260 --> 00:00:50,010
Thanks
for letting me borrow your makeup and everything.

22
00:00:50,010 --> 00:00:51,010
Mhm.

23
00:00:51,010 --> 00:00:52,720
Pick something to wear from here.

24
00:00:53,260 --> 00:00:54,760
This one's so cool.

25
00:00:54,760 --> 00:00:57,850
You can wear whatever you like,
but for an occasion like this...

26
00:00:59,180 --> 00:01:00,600
I think this one would suit you better.

27
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:02,560
- Then I'll try it on.
- Okay.

28
00:01:05,900 --> 00:01:07,360
What's wrong?

29
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:08,860
It's embarrassing, isn't it?

30
00:01:10,860 --> 00:01:12,490
Am I wearing this right?

31
00:01:12,490 --> 00:01:13,780
You've got it wrong.

32
00:01:13,780 --> 00:01:17,660
You even messed up the buttons.
Are you a kid?

33
00:01:17,660 --> 00:01:19,120
Thanks.

34
00:01:23,250 --> 00:01:28,880
(It really is that scar.
Could Makoto be my...)
